    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with plenty of character and a surprisingly composed chassis for its age. Engine pulls cleanly, transmission engages as it should, and the suspension/brake setup delivers a confident, road-ready feel. Cosmetically it shows wear consistent with a well-used driver, but that also makes it an ideal budget-friendly commuter, project platform, or backup vehicle. If you want something affordable that still feels mechanically usable and worth improving, this one has real potential.",
