      "description": "Turn the key and imagine the possibilities\u2014this car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that speaks to weekend tinkerers, first-time project seekers, or anyone who appreciates a machine with a story still left to tell. Its presence has a rugged charm, and with the right vision, it could become a dependable budget runabout, a rewarding fixer-upper, or the perfect parts donor for a bigger dream. If you love the idea of giving a car a second chapter, this one offers a low-cost entry point and plenty of potential.",
